    <h3 id="Acquiring-Role-Specific-Skills"><b>Why Acquiring Role-Specific Skills Important For Data Engineers?</b></h3>
    
        
    <p style="text-align: justify;">
        To secure a promising position as Azure Data Engineer in top companies, a candidate must also specialize in role-specific skills. These role-specific skills include the following;
    </p>
    
    <ul style="padding-left: 40px;text-align: justify;">
        <li>
           The candidate should have proper understanding of data structure and algorithm.  
        </li><br>
        <li>
           He/she should have in-depth understanding of big data tools like Hadoop.
        </li><br>
        <li>
           Candidates should learn SQL as this will help them understand the database and the structures underlying them.  
        </li><br>
        <li>
        	The aspirants should also have an understanding that most tools for storage and processing of data use programming languages. Therefore, the aspirants should focus on learning programming languages like Java, Python, Scala, etc.  
